  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[博文页增加Recent Posts等侧边栏]]></title>
    <link href="https://qiuhaidong.github.io/blog/2022/02/21/post-html-add-sidebar-about-recent-posts/"/>
    <updated>2022-02-21T21:43:06+08:00</updated>
    <id>https://qiuhaidong.github.io/blog/2022/02/21/post-html-add-sidebar-about-recent-posts</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>博客根目录，文件<code>index.html</code>，找到<code>Recent Posts</code>这一大段内容，复制，打开<code>_layouts/post.html</code>，找到：</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&lt;div class="right"&gt;
</span><span class='line'>    &lt;div class="wrap"&gt;</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>复制到其后面。</p>

<p>因为只复制一段老是有错，现在我是把<code>index.html</code>的<code>&lt;div class="right"&gt;</code>右边栏一直到最后的内容，代替了<code>_layouts/post.html</code>右边栏一直到最后的内容。</p>

